sequenceDiagram
    participant PublicChannel
    participant Receiver
    participant Blockchain
    
    PublicChannel->>Receiver: Detect new encrypted payload<br/>(via relay or direct monitoring)
    Receiver->>Blockchain: Verify entropy source<br/>(transaction or block)
    Blockchain-->>Receiver: Confirms entropy validity
    Receiver->>Receiver: Derive identical key<br/>using same algorithm
    Receiver->>Receiver: Decrypt and verify message<br/>authentication tag
    Receiver->>Receiver: Display message to user
